SPELL NAME  : Cure All Wounds
SPELL SYNTAX: Caw <target>
SPELL COST  : 125 SP
DESCRIPTION : Through the love of Mitra and the strength of your faith, the
	      Cleric has the ability to provide massive healing for those who
	      have met with disaster. Though draining to invoke, Mitra will
	      provide the unfortunate soul with nearly complete healing.
